<l>uṟāa tavarkaṇṭa kaṇṇu mavaraic </l>
<l>ceṟāareṉac cēṟiyeṉ ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my soul! although you have known him who does not love me, still do you go to him, saying "he will not be displeased."</l>
